hether there is an overrun, change in venue or shift in schedule, an event app can help you communicate these changes in a matter of seconds.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-349434b elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"349434b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Updating Your Content Digitally<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-00123b7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"00123b7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Last minute changes? No need to worry.\u00a0If there are any changes, you can amend it from the back end and it will be reflected in real-time. Changes in your schedules? You can drag and drop the content block to rearrange your schedule easily.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f486df8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"f486df8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"768\" height=\"378\" src=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2021\/06\/1-13.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2664\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2021\/06\/1-13.jpg 768w, https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/5\/2021\/06\/1-13-300x148.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d13c124 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d13c124\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Push Notifications for Important Announcements<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-baf4933 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"baf4933\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Change in location after a break? Afraid that your attendees might not notice the changes that you have updated? You can send a push notification to your selected group of users to notify them of the changes.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Last minute changes? Even the most experienced event organisers will encounter this during an event. Pulling off a successful event requires countless [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3001,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[135,131,133],"tags":[110],"class_list":["post-2656","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-event-news","category-how-to-tutorials","category-industry-insights","tag-event-apps"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2656","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/micepad.co\/tw\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http